      "title": null,
      "content": "Twitter 官方开始打击这种程序化的内容搬运，有些喜欢抄东西不转发的，可以准备好了。 Nikita Bier (@nikitabier) Over the past month, we have identified a number of large accounts that have been programmatically reuploading content from smaller accounts to game the revenue share program and circumvent crediting the original author. We are now identifying these posts and allocating the impressions entirely to the creator. If you have insightful commentary about a post, we recommend using the Share Video or Quote feature to ensure your posts are properly attributed. — https://nitter.net/nikitabier/status/2058020001823793265#m",
      "url": "https://x.com/op7418/status/2058806244295774350",
      "images": null,
